{
  "text": "The Tcra Locus The Tcra locus contains $100 Va (TRAV) gene segments and 61 Ja (TRAJ) gene segments (Figure 3, diagram) . Initial rearrangements involve preferential use of more 3 0 Va gene segments and focus on the most 5 0 Ja gene segments because of the strong T early-a (TEA) promoter that lies 2 kb upstream of TRAJ61 [CITATION_1] .",
